<!-- Node: "Missing Tutorials" -->
<div class="body_box_header">Missing Tutorials</div>
<div class="body_box"><small>Submitted by <a href="http://www.gamedesign.net/user/view/31" title="View user profile.">mazemaster</a> on Tuesday, May 25, 2004 - 08:08</small><br /><br />
Several of our editing tutorials are MIA at the moment. Sorry about that, we are trying to fix it. If you can't find a tutorial that you think RUST used to have please let us know <a href="http://forums.gamedesign.net/viewtopic.php?p=44133#44133">in this thread</a> in the forums. <br />
<br />
If you got to this main page through a broken tutorial link, its a good indication that the tutorial is missing.<br />
<br />
<a href="http://forums.gamedesign.net/viewtopic.php?p=44133#44133">http://forums.gamedesign.net/viewtopic.php?p=44133#44133</a>
